<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idf009983b-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s7424"><num value="7424">§ 7424.</num><heading> Regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary may issue such regulations as may be necessary to carry out this subchapter and the power vested in the Secretary under this subchapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idf009983c-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/104/127/tV/s525">Pub. L. 104–127, title V, § 525</ref>, <date date="1996-04-04">Apr. 4, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/1048">110 Stat. 1048</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
